// Signing.local.example.xcconfig — template for local code-signing.
//
// Copy this file to `Signing.local.xcconfig` (gitignored) and set your Apple
// Developer Team ID. This is required only to test mobile push from the
// command line (`npm run ios` / `xcodebuild` / CI). Running from Xcode injects
// your team automatically, so the GUI works without this file.
//
//   cp Signing.local.example.xcconfig Signing.local.xcconfig
//
// Find your 10-character Team ID via either:
//   * Apple Developer portal → Membership → Team ID, or
//   * security find-identity -p codesigning -v   (the "(TEAMID)" suffix)
//
// A free personal team is sufficient for Simulator push registration.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
